item.title: About
item.description: Algiers R User is group for R programming language user, founded on July 2020. This group strives to connect the R user community, in Algiers and near Algiers to promote the sharing membership knowledge and their experiences. Founding members: Wassim Medour: Mohamed El Fodil Ihaddaden: PhD candidate in Economics. Kamila Benadrouche: Teacher at University M’Hamed Bouggera of Boumerdes. Nassim Kaddour: Adel Fiala: Hani Bounoua: Support Research Engineer at CERIST. Join us: Kind reminder: The notoriety of a community is made by its members.
